{"tid":1057522,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯原來愛車路士！二兒子穿藍軍波衫","createTime":"2019-03-12T02:56:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T04:52:16.000Z","uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bbca8cf85a2282c173991814c36bfbfac7907189","tid":1057522,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T02:56:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2019/03/12/f/faff520d77732e057fee105987ccc82e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2019%2F03%2F12%2Ff%2Ffaff520d77732e057fee105987ccc82e.jpg&h=25d77016&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3月10日是美斯的小兒子Ciro一歲生日，有趣的是二哥馬特奧是穿著車路士的波衫參加了弟弟的生日派對。<br />\n<br />\n通過美斯親戚的Instagram，可以看見馬特奧身穿車路士的波衫。<br />\n<br />\n  《世界體育報》認為這是因為美斯一家和法比加斯一家關係非常好，法比加斯曾為藍軍效力5個賽季，不久前才離開並加盟摩納哥。"},{"pid":"66fbe51038e450cc0a33808b459b0ddc950c29e4","tid":1057522,"uid":35176,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:03:42.000Z","msg":"14年ig follow車嘅時候 咪傳過去車仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c65adcc5fb07f8eb38f5f29b34692ca71330def","tid":1057522,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:20:04.000Z","msg":"高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0641a654a7735bf765274ee53d6bd3e7a850da88","tid":1057522,"uid":129733,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:57:27.000Z","msg":"證明bb先鐘意我轟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387290dbce6c3ae705e4b3eca80e0ba72fa6f4a2","tid":1057522,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T04:04:06.000Z","msg":"就算美斯肯去, 車仔有錢果時都買唔到佢, 依家連人工都唔夠錢俾啦"},{"pid":"9b3b3e22bbdd9040299817e7a2e4d5727ee43005","tid":105